{"tid":1028567,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"高級消防隊長涉向3下屬借7萬　遭廉署起訴周四應訊","createTime":"2019-02-19T14:53:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-19T15:02:26.000Z","uid":121464,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"1edd49cc73cd969cfb095d5c3c9bda34cb254279","tid":1028567,"uid":121464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T14:53:56.000Z","msg":"廉政公署今日(19日)落案起訴1名消防處高級消防隊長，控告他涉嫌未經許可向3名下屬索取及接受共7萬港元貸款。53歲被告吳麟光現被控3項罪名，即2項訂明人員索取利益，及1項訂明人員索取及接受利益。被告已獲准保釋，本周四(21日)在東區裁判法院答辯。 <br />\n<br />\n被告於案發時為消防處高級消防隊長，被調派至海務及離島區工作。其中2項控罪指，被告涉嫌於2017年3月30日，未得行政長官一般或特別許可而向2名為其下屬的消防隊目，各索取一筆3萬港元貸款；以及涉嫌於2017年3月1日至5月31日期間某日，向1名為其直屬下屬的消防總隊目索取及接受一筆1萬港元貸款。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pqiNmsu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpqiNmsu.png&h=9d6c21d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190219/mobile/bkn-20190219165131695-0219_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190219%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20190219165131695-0219_00822_001.html&d=xc0devjmTjk1MRQhR5SRZ6Ggm0NOSfkDZSs230CVm%2Fs%3D&h=b26e4d8a\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190219/mobile/bkn-20190219165131695-0219_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n海務及離島區: 水位？<br />\nsfo: 人工應該60-80k?<br />\n究竟要賭幾大 先要問下屬借錢？"},{"pid":"abc468210032b519b55231bcda6448d1f0fd4c57","tid":1028567,"uid":20291,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T14:59:48.000Z","msg":"同事之間借錢係唔得？"},{"pid":"5d7a1d76f6f1e592dad9a942bb99313e8e1b6383","tid":1028567,"uid":11523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"abc468210032b519b55231bcda6448d1f0fd4c57","tid":1028567,"uid":20291,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T14:59:48.000Z","msg":"同事之間借錢係唔得？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T15:02:23.000Z","msg":"上級唔可以問下屬借錢"},{"pid":"63e6922dfdd3e02c77d537c0c4bfc3a6bcf4328a","tid":1028567,"uid":17646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sco